    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSeptember 4 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t Tidemark Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n1220 Shoppers Row\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tCampbell River,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV9W 2C8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t$33.00\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tSeating Plan\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tRandy’s Cheeseburger Picnic (Trailer Park Boys)\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\tThe Diamond Mine Agency Presents:\nRandy’s Cheeseburger Picnic (Trailer Park Boys) Comedy Tour \nThe lovable character, Randy, from Trailer Park Boys fame, brings his hilarious comedy act Randy‘s Cheeseburger Picnic for a night of laughter. A comedy act filled with Trailer Park Boys’ shenanigans, songs, contests and prizes will surely lift your spirits. Tell your frown to Frig Off and get ready for a good time with Randy Bobandy himself!\nhttps://www.facebook.com/officialpatroach\nhttps://www.facebook.com/trailerparkboys\nTickets:$33.00 Admission, $100.00 VIP Meet & Greet Add On (+applicable taxes & fees)  \nThis is a 19+ event\nVIP Add On Includes: 1 Hour Preshow Hangout With Randy Including Trailer Park Q&A, Photo With Randy and an Autographed Tour Poster!\nVIP MEET AND GREET 6:00PM\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShare this:\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Facebook\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on X\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Linkedin\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Email\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Pinterest\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tOrganizer\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tThe Diamond Mine Agency\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEvent Details\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t September 4 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $33.00 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: At the Tidemark\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t Ian Maksin – Songs of Love & Peace\n\t\t\tHighwaymen Show – Great Outlaws Tribute \n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\t"
