    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSeptember 11 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t Tidemark Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n1220 Shoppers Row\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tCampbell River,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV9W 2C8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t$38.00\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tSeating Plan\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDiabolo Dance Theatre of Taiwan\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\tA Spectacular Fusion of Culture and Innovation Connecting to the World\nThe Diabolo Dance Theatre Established in 1986, is a world-renowned performing arts group from Taiwan. They are famous for their unique “Diabolo Dance” performance, which elevates the traditional Chinese yo-yo (diabolo) into a mesmerizing contemporary stage art.\nThey seamlessly blend diabolos with modern dance, acrobatics, theatre, and stunning visual multimedia. Through dynamic choreography and emotional storytelling, their performances transcend language and cultural barriers, captivating audiences of all ages globally.\nThe troupe has toured over 30 countries and performed more than 3,000 shows. Their prestigious appearances include the New Lincoln Centre, World Expo, and major theatres worldwide, served as a shining cultural ambassador for Taiwan.\nTickets: $38.00 Adults, $33.00 Senior/Student, $23.00 Child 10-, $33.00 Groups 10+ (+applicable taxes & fees)\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShare this:\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Facebook\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on X\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Linkedin\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Email\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Pinterest\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tOrganizer\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCV Multicultural Society/Maple Pool Campsite\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEvent Details\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t September 11 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $38.00 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: At the Tidemark\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\