    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSeptember 18 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t Tidemark Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n1220 Shoppers Row\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tCampbell River,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV9W 2C8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t$59.00\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tSeating Plan\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tFleetwood Magic\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\tFleetwood Magic Tribute Show masterfully transports audiences in sound and time through a musical journey performing Fleetwood Mac’s greatest hits from the 60’s to the 80’s, authentically recreating the sound, style and mystique of Fleetwood Mac’s most iconic line-up.\nWith stunning vintage costumes, precise vocals, period-accurate instrumentation, and captivating on-stage personas, Fleetwood Magic delivers a live experience that reminds fans why Fleetwood Mac remains legendary.\nRelive timeless classics like “Rhiannon,” “Dreams,” “You Make Loving Fun,” “Say You Love Me,” “The Chain,” “Go Your Own Way.” Listeners have come to realize the ‘Rumours’ are true – Fleetwood Magic does indeed, deliver the magic!\nConsistently playing sold out shows to audiences across the Vancouver Lower Mainland and Canada, their shows have become a must-see event for Fleetwood Mac music fans of all ages!\nFor more information about Fleetwood Magic, please visit: www.fleetwoodmagic.ca\nTickets: $59 Admission, Groups 6+ Receive 10% off (+applicable taxes & fees)\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShare this:\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Facebook\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on X\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Linkedin\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Email\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Pinterest\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tOrganizer\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEvent Details\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t September 18 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $59.00 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: At the Tidemark\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\