    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSeptember 22 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t Tidemark Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n1220 Shoppers Row\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tCampbell River,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV9W 2C8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t$57.00\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tSeating Plan\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tThe Alan Jackson Experience\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\tThe Alan Jackson Experience\nPerformed by Aaron Halliday, a two-time ISSA Entertainer of the Year Award winner and Canadian/ Nashville recording artist, and presented by ASH Entertainment, brings an internationally recognized tribute to Alan Jackson, featuring Award-winning musicians.\nThis show is a precise recreation of an Alan Jackson concert, boasting an authentic look, stage presence, and sound that will transport you to the real thing. Prepare yourself for an energetic and entertaining performance that will have you singing along to ‘Good Time’ and reminiscing about the past with ‘Remember When.’\nAs an added bonus, ticket holders can meet the artists in the lobby during intermission.\nCheck out the video below to get a feel for the show:\n\nTickets: $57.00 Adult, $53.00 Senior/Student (+applicable taxes & fees)\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShare this:\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Facebook\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on X\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Linkedin\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Email\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Pinterest\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tOrganizer\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tASH Entertainment\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEvent Details\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t September 22 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $57.00 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: At the Tidemark\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Navigation\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t PWR/UP  AC/DC Tribute\n\t\t\tSIXX PAXX – Europe’s #1 Male Revue \n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\t"
