    "https://schema.org/mainContentOfPage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\tSeptember 23 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Venue \n\t\n\t\t\t\t Tidemark Theatre \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n1220 Shoppers Row\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tCampbell River,\n\n\tBC\n\n\tV9W 2C8\n\n\tCanada\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+ Google Map\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t$55.00\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tSeating Plan\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tSIXX PAXX – Europe’s #1 Male Revue\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\tSIXX PAXX DREAMS TOUR 2026/27\nWHEN FANTASIES COME TRUE\nClose your eyes and imagine your wildest night out—then watch it come to life. The SIXX PAXX DREAMS TOUR arrives in 2026/27, taking the internationally acclaimed sensation to the biggest stages they’ve ever played.\nThis all-new production turns up the heat with more seduction, more  passion, and more unforgettable moments—featuring electrifying\nchoreography, live vocals, and a high-impact show that begins like a dream and stays with you long after the final bow.\nPerfect for a girls’ night out, birthday celebration, or bachelorette party, SIXX PAXX delivers an interactive, high-energy experience\nwhere fantasy meets world-class performance.\nTickets: $99.00 VIP includes Meet & Greet, $69.00 Premium, $55.00 Admission (includes GST + applicable fees)\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tShare this:\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Facebook\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on X\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Linkedin\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Email\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tShare on Pinterest\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tOrganizer\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\tOrganizer\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tForrest Jones Entertainment\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tEvent Details\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\n\t Details \n\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tDate:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t September 23 \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tTime:\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t7:30 pm - 9:30 pm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tCost:\n\t\t\t\t $55.00 \n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\tEvent Category: At the Tidemark\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBuy Tickets\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\